ining a\nphysical model of the IISM and current pulsar timing results, we also constrain\n$\\Omega=225\\pm3^\\circ$ and $i=86.46\\pm0.05^\\circ$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Oct 2022 01:54:40 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-09"}
