eal-world multi-robot field\ndeployments where we show improvements of the onboard system up to 90\\% and can\nrecover the onboard estimation from localization failures and even from the\ndegeneracies within its estimation.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Oct 2022 09:21:12 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 2 Nov 2022 14:00:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-03"}
