rable\nimprovement in novelty detection over state-of-the-art methods on MNIST and\nCaltech-256 datasets.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Oct 2022 11:09:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-11-01"}
