mplar. We argue that scribal takeovers in the exemplar impacts\nthe practice of the copying scribe, while transitions to a different content\nmatter cause little to no effect.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Oct 2022 14:40:25 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 30 Oct 2022 14:09:04 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Fri, 10 Feb 2023 13:53:09 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Thu, 6 Apr 2023 15:28:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-04-07"}
