\ninstanton chain complexes of $Y$ and $Y'$. However, it does define a chain map\nbetween the instanton chain complex of $Y$ and a sort of suspension of the\ninstanton chain complex of $Y'$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 25 Oct 2022 14:55:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-26"}
